{
  "stem": "15174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Leon, this friend of mine who had been on the also I told you about before, and I decided that we would go to one of the villages up on the mountain where almost nobody went, and we would see if we could find [LAUGH] some food.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean here we were, we were 11-- he was 12 then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- yeah, 11.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess I was 8 or 9, and he was 10 or 11.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here we were going to get food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we walk up to this village-- it was probably two or three miles-- and we were actually able to buy some flour, I think half a dozen eggs, and some honey, and something else.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our parents had given us-- imagine-- trusted us-- and trusted us with money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, we-- we-- we got all this stuff and we brought it home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, you can't imagine what our parents were like when they saw that we had brought the stuff.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean my mother was ecstatic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She said, 'Oh, my god!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm gonna be able to bake a cake for the holiday!' [LAUGH] It was-- it was just-- it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Imagine, you know, here we are, we can go to the store and buy whatever we want.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it's hard to imagine just not being able to find food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I also learned how to ride a bicycle there because the teacher had a bike and she allowed some of the kids to use it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I learned how to ride a bike in-- in [INAUDIBLE] also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was some nice things that were-- that I have memories of.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
